channel.title: Really strange hosting problem
channel.description:
i am currently hosting my server, so i start my server and every1 gets on nice and easy people between 5 - 45 people are normaly on. but then for some reason my server start up screen it says [code]Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?[/code] whitch stops any1 from this point coming in. people already on my server stay on until they log of when they then cant log on..
so if any1 has any ideas that would helpful[br][size=1]Posted on: February 17, 2007, 03:30:25 PM[/size][hr][code] Starting Cookscape on 0.0.0.0:43594 ClientHandler: Accepted from [took out] ClientHandler: Accepted from [took out] Client type: low memory version UserId: 39033905 o0aqua0o is signing onto server. Client type: low memory version UserId: 13462146 thekidkiller is signing onto server. config\objects.cfg: file not found. Summoning: Loading monsters from Summon.cfg ... Summoning: Loaded 24 monsters from Summon.cfg! Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?[/code] that what is what it looks like btw i took out the ppls ips
